          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <actionDate>2016-06-08</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Offshore Wind Incentives for New Development Act or the Offshore WIND Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand the tax credit for investment in energy property to include a qualified offshore wind property until January 1, 2026. Under the bill, a qualified offshore wind property is an offshore facility that uses wind to produce electricity, excluding certain small wind energy property which uses a small wind turbine to generate electricity. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
